{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21b6bdfb9c","title":"关于向归国华侨传达《中共中央通知》问题的补充通知","origin":"（根据中央文件原件打印）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9ae0c073b","index":0,"year":1971,"month":11,"day":30,"articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0f95027971","type":"title","text":"关于向归国华侨传达《中共中央通知》问题的补充通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"7ac60f5f28","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区党委，各大军区、各省军区、各野战军党委，军委各总部、各军、兵种党委，中央和国务院各部委领导小组、党的核心小组：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"23e9b134be","type":"paragraph","text":"关于对久居国内有固定职业的归国华侨传达林陈反党集团问题，当时为了保密的需要，曾做了一些规定，这是必要的。但他们和当地工人一起工作和生活，由于传达和做法不一致，也引起一些意见，为了更好地把团结教育华侨的工作做好，中央作如下补充通知：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"7eaf2f878f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、在中央[1971]69号文件下达前，已与当地职工一起听了传达的华侨，仍同职工一起学习讨论。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"6a2cb5dbd7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、尚未传达的单位，符合条件的，可同本单位的职工一起听传达和讨论。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"f9b25c2162","type":"paragraph","text":"三、已单独组织华侨进行了三个文件传达的，可补充传达中发[1971]61号、62号、64号、67号四个文件。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"71f3636062","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中央一九七一年十一月三十日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"45eb9fc68f","type":"paragraph","text":"（此件发至县、团级）","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"de14db81f3","type":"appellation","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"a14a6a8898","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅                       一九七一年十二月三日发出","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"},{"id":"41c19c9180","type":"appellation","text":"____________________________________________________________________","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c"}],"page":{"id":"be8b202030","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"21b6bdfb9c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}